## Build

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/memvid/memvid.git
cd memvid
```

Build in debug mode:

```bash
cargo build
```

Build in release mode (optimized):

```bash
cargo build --release
```

Build with specific features:

```bash
cargo build --release --features "lex,vec,temporal_track"
```

